  "title": "Sales Consultant",
  "description": "<ul><li>Promote the company’s treatments and products in a professional and customer-centric manner</li><li>Conduct professional body analysis, and recommend suitable treatments, service and products based on individual needs</li><li>Clearly explain treatment and product benefits, usage, and expected outcomes to customers</li><li>Maintain a strong working knowledge of TCM treatment, service and products.</li><li>Deliver consistently high standards of customer service and care</li><li>Build and maintain long-term relationships with existing and potential customers to support sales growth</li><li>Achieve and exceed individual sales targets</li><li>Assist customers with appointment scheduling, rescheduling, and basic follow-ups</li><li>Handle basic administrative duties, including processing and recording sales</li></ul><p>Working Hour:-</p><p>Mon - Fri: 9:45am - 8pm</p><p>Sat - Sun, PH: 8:45am - 5pm</p><p>Working Area:-</p><p>Central ; East Area</p>",
